Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.86,0:00:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,把雪莉料酒藏起来不给老爸用吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Hiding the cooking sherry from Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.94,0:00:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我要做面包 Daria\N{\fnArial\fs18}I'm going to make some bread, Daria.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.01,0:00:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,这儿不是有超市么?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Isn't that what supermarkets are for?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.27,0:00:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeager一家人周末要过来呢\N{\fnArial\fs18}The Yeagers are coming for the weekend,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.13,0:01:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能用超市买的面包招待他们\N{\fnArial\fs18}and I can't serve them store-bought bread.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.59,0:01:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,为啥?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.60,0:01:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我有25年没见过他们了\N{\fnArial\fs18}I haven't seen them for twenty five years,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.66,0:01:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,比方说他们会见到一个截然不同的Helen\N{\fnArial\fs18}and let's just say they know a different Helen.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.86,0:01:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,一个做燕麦南瓜籽面包很拿手的Helen\N{\fnArial\fs18}A Helen famous for her oatmeal pumpkin seed loaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.32,0:01:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你把现在这个Helen怎么了?\N{\fnArial\fs18}And just what have you done with this Helen?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.87,0:01:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,他们来啦\N{\fnArial\fs18}They're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.17,0:01:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,希望他们不会觉得我有很大变化\N{\fnArial\fs18}I hope they don't think I've changed too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.59,0:01:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,做你自己就好了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Just be yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.83,0:01:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,这是你一直贯彻给我的\N{\fnArial\fs18}That's what you've always told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.43,0:01:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我真懊悔说过那种蠢话\N{\fnArial\fs18}I could kick myself for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.79,0:01:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么车?\N{\fnArial\fs18}What kind of car is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.82,0:01:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,那不是车\N{\fnArial\fs18}That's not a car.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.08,0:01:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,是时光机\N{\fnArial\fs18}It's a time machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.81,0:01:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Willow Coyote\N{\fnArial\fs18}Willow! Coyote!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.72,0:01:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 Helen\N{\fnArial\fs18}Wow, Helen!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.18,0:01:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- 亲 - 伙计\N{\fnArial\fs18}- Man! - My man!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.91,0:01:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你一点儿都没变\N{\fnArial\fs18}You haven't changed a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.73,0:01:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你呀 瞧瞧你呀\N{\fnArial\fs18}And you! Well, just look at you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.71,0:01:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呦 怎么Leary也一点都没变\N{\fnArial\fs18}Why, even Leary is exactly the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.52,0:01:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,快过来 孩儿\N{\fnArial\fs18}Come here, boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.70,0:01:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,还记得老Jake么?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Don't you remember old Jake?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.18,0:01:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 那肯定不是Leary\N{\fnArial\fs18}Wait, that can't be Leary.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.78,0:01:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,它现在都快有30了吧\N{\fnArial\fs18}He'd be almost thirty by now!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.74,0:01:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这是Leary三世\N{\fnArial\fs18}This is Leary number three.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.97,0:02:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我们隔段时间就要替换原来那只\N{\fnArial\fs18}We had to replace the original a few times.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.30,0:02:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs26\an8}美国著名心理学家 作家 以其晚年对迷幻药的研究而知名
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.30,0:02:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,要是你能替换掉蒂莫西·利里就更好啦 对吧 亲?\N{\fnArial\fs18}If only you could do that with Timothy Leary, huh, man?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.66,0:02:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,他们已经在着手了\N{\fnArial\fs18}They're working on it, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.66,0:02:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 她俩可无可取代\N{\fnArial\fs18}Well, these two are irreplaceable.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.64,0:02:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的乖女 Quinn和Daria\N{\fnArial\fs18}Our girls, Quinn and Daria.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.13,0:02:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你的灵魂很苍老\N{\fnArial\fs18}You have a very old soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.86,0:02:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,只是看起来比年龄成熟点\N{\fnArial\fs18}It just looks mature for its age.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.60,0:02:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么复古行头 还是他们就这么打扮?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Is this a retro thing, or are they serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.74,0:02:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- 先把行李拿进去吧亲 - 我们轻装旅行\N{\fnArial\fs18}- Let's get your bags, man! - We travel light.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.03,0:02:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,在脑子里\N{\fnArial\fs18}In the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.22,0:02:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,在得到更多良好共鸣前 我得离开这儿\N{\fnArial\fs18}I gotta get out of here before I catch any more good vibes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.42,0:02:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Daria 你不能把我扔在这儿和那些... 那些雅皮士在一起\N{\fnArial\fs18}Daria, you can't leave me here with those, those... yuppies!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.42,0:02:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs26\an8}雅皮士不颓废 不关心社会问题 只追求舒适和彰显自我性格
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.14,0:02:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,雅皮士是八十年代的产物\N{\fnArial\fs18}Yuppies are from the Eighties.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.01,0:02:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,那应该怎么称呼...\N{\fnArial\fs18}So what do you call people
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.34,0:02:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,那些奇装异服又大肆谈论爱与和平的人?\N{\fnArial\fs18}with funny outfits who talk about peace and love and stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.90,0:02:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,星舰迷吧 不管怎样 我们中得有人留下来\N{\fnArial\fs18}Trekkies. Anyway, one of us should stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.84,0:02:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,这是能进一步了解爸妈的难得机会\N{\fnArial\fs18}It's a rare opportunity to learn more about Mom and Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.77,0:02:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,为嘛我们会想那样做?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Why would we want to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.86,0:02:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,这样以后就能用来对付他们了\N{\fnArial\fs18}To use against them later.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.69,0:02:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,挖到丑闻的话 给你20块\N{\fnArial\fs18}Twenty bucks if you dig up some dirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.91,0:02:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思 我有约了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Sorry, I have a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.12,0:02:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你不干 我也不干\N{\fnArial\fs18}You're getting out of this, so am I.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.94,0:02:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ethan 快来会会姑娘们\N{\fnArial\fs18}Ethan! Come meet the girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.38,0:03:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你说要给我20块吧?\N{\fnArial\fs18}You said twenty, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.65,0:03:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Zappa数位声道... Zappa模拟声道\N{\fnArial\fs18}appa digital... Zappa analog.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.65,0:03:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs26\an8}Zappa: 弗兰克·扎帕 美国六十年代摇滚乐先锋人物之一
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.88,0:03:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得听起来都差不多\N{\fnArial\fs18}Sounds the same to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.98,0:03:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,那你还敢自称是音乐家?\N{\fnArial\fs18}And you call yourself a musician?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.23,0:03:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,才没呢 我自称声音的翻译家\N{\fnArial\fs18}No, I call myself an interpreter of sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.18,0:03:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,最高机密实验?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Top secret experiment?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.84,0:03:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我爸妈让我把他们的旧唱片拿去跳蚤市场卖了\N{\fnArial\fs18}My parents gave me their old records to sell at the flea market,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.24,0:03:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,不过Trent说他想要\N{\fnArial\fs18}but now Trent wants to keep 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.81,0:03:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,这可是黑胶唱片情怀 亲\N{\fnArial\fs18}It's the warmth of vinyl, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.89,0:03:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,跟你说 这是强烈的乐音\N{\fnArial\fs18}I'm telling you, it's a richer tone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.59,0:03:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你调到收音机去了啦\N{\fnArial\fs18}You're tuned to the radio.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.28,0:03:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我还纳闷为什么Zapa要卖炸鱼柳\N{\fnArial\fs18}I wondered why Zappa was selling fish sticks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.37,0:03:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,跳蚤市场嘛? 要不要帮忙呀?\N{\fnArial\fs18}The flea market, huh? Need any help?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.05,0:03:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我们七点钟就得开摊了\N{\fnArial\fs18}We have to be there by 7:00 to set up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.90,0:03:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题 Daria就是只早起的鸟儿\N{\fnArial\fs18}No problem. Daria's an early bird.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.54,0:03:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么事比看日出更好啦\N{\fnArial\fs18}There's nothing like watching the sun rise,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.46,0:03:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,除了看太阳反向落下外\N{\fnArial\fs18}except watching the sun set in reverse.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.88,0:03:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,接得好呀 Daria\N{\fnArial\fs18}Good one, Daria.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.26,0:03:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,谢了哟\N{\fnArial\fs18}Mmm, umm, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.97,0:03:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,好啦 这次让我们来反接插头\N{\fnArial\fs18}Okay, this time, let's reverse the polarity of the plug.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.80,0:03:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我来面西而立\N{\fnArial\fs18}And I'll stand facing west.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.09,0:03:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,好哒\N{\fnArial\fs18}Ok cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.32,0:04:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你秀逗吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Are you nuts?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.60,0:04:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 你随时都能回家 和雅皮士互换优格配方嘛\N{\fnArial\fs18}Hey, you could always go on home and swap yogurt recipes with the Yeagers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.87,0:04:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我的优格怎么了?\N{\fnArial\fs18}And what's wrong with my yogurt recipe?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.23,0:04:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你得感谢我\N{\fnArial\fs18}You should thank me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.28,0:04:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,这可是你能和Trent共享宝贵时间的好机会\N{\fnArial\fs18}It's a chance for you to spend some quality time with Trent.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.71,0:04:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,而且今年的跳蚤市场超浪漫的\N{\fnArial\fs18}And the flea market is so romantic this time of year.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.80,0:04:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,听说草头娃娃们开得风华正茂\N{\fnArial\fs18}I hear the Chia Pets are in bloom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.25,0:04:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,好啦 就跳蚤市场了\N{\fnArial\fs18}All right, so, the flea market.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.63,0:04:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我们去定了\N{\fnArial\fs18}We're there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.10,0:04:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 现在试试我站在铝箔上的效果\N{\fnArial\fs18}Okay, now let's try the thing where I stand on the aluminum foil.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.51,0:04:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,过去的20年里 我们都通过邮寄 贩卖大麻做的吊床\N{\fnArial\fs18}So, for the past twelve years, we've been selling hammocks of hemp by mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.33,0:04:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,由于大麻加工技术有了新进展\N{\fnArial\fs18}And with all the recent breakthroughs in hemp processing,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.67,0:04:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,这会是最让人兴奋的一年啦\N{\fnArial\fs18}this could be our most exciting year yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.69,0:04:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 这可真有意思\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh! That's fascinating.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.32,0:04:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Quinn 你今晚不是有约会么?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Quinn, didn't you have a date tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.86,0:04:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我让Stacy替我去了\N{\fnArial\fs18}I got Stacy to fill in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.27,0:04:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你喜欢运动是吧 小伙子?\N{\fnArial\fs18}You into sports, my man?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.08,0:04:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Ethan?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Ethan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.22,0:04:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我们觉得这星球上的攻击性行为已经够多了\N{\fnArial\fs18}We think there's enough aggressive behavior on the planet
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.18,0:04:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,还不算上建立更多所谓的"良性竞争"\N{\fnArial\fs18}without creating more with quote unquote "healthy competition."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.22,0:04:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ethan要是准备好了 就会去攀岩\N{\fnArial\fs18}Ethan's gonna rock climb, when he's ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.26,0:04:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,没所谓 棒球也行\N{\fnArial\fs18}Whatever. Peas.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.14,0:05:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,面包是不是用手发面的 一吃就知道\N{\fnArial\fs18}You can always tell when a bread isn't hand-kneaded.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.35,0:05:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,人工揉的面团有更多的灵气\N{\fnArial\fs18}Hand-kneaded bread has more soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.26,0:05:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,素食的东西我吃不饱\N{\fnArial\fs18}This veggie stuff never fills me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.90,0:05:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,有人要来个汉堡么?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Anyone want a burger?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.12,0:05:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 公平点嘛\N{\fnArial\fs18}Hey, fair's fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.72,0:05:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,总有哪天 我们都会变成蠕虫的食物\N{\fnArial\fs18}We'll all be worm food someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.43,0:05:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Jake\N{\fnArial\fs18}Jake!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.21,0:05:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,这是万物因果循环 Helen\N{\fnArial\fs18}It's the circle of life, Helen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.34,0:05:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你知道吗亲 你有点咄咄逼人了- 我才没有\N{\fnArial\fs18}- You know, man, you've become kind of aggressive. - I have not!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.03,0:05:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,- 都是吃荤的错 - 才不是\N{\fnArial\fs18}- It's the meat. - Is not!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.55,0:05:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你以前那种成熟又随性的态度怎么变了?\N{\fnArial\fs18}What ever happened to the mellow, let-it-be attitude you used to have?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.87,0:05:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Jake?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Jake?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.27,0:05:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧 大家\N{\fnArial\fs18}Come on, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.80,0:05:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们集中所有的正能量\N{\fnArial\fs18}If we focus all our positive energy,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.88,0:05:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就能让五角大楼从平地升起\N{\fnArial\fs18}we can make the Pentagon rise up off the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.88,0:05:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs26\an8}1967反文化运动里雅皮士意用精神力来搬动五角大楼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.68,0:05:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,升起来呀 擦\N{\fnArial\fs18}Rise, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.90,0:05:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,愚蠢的五边形建筑\N{\fnArial\fs18}Stupid five-sided building.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.21,0:05:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,还记得我们的小租房吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Remember our group house?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.58,0:05:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,还不懂么?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Don't you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.65,0:05:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,所谓有见识的男人都在压迫女人\N{\fnArial\fs18}So-called enlightened dudes are oppressing women,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.15,0:05:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,就像社会平定动荡一样\N{\fnArial\fs18}just like society is putting down the movement.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.49,0:06:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要帮助 现在就要\N{\fnArial\fs18}I want some help, and I want it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.96,0:06:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 听起来妹子们好像在闹解放呢\N{\fnArial\fs18}Wow. Sounds like the girls are getting liberated.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.37,0:06:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,真酷\N{\fnArial\fs18}Cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.05,0:06:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,后来在大家散伙了以后\N{\fnArial\fs18}And then, after you guys split,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.07,0:06:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我们涂画包装了一辆公车 开进了沙漠\N{\fnArial\fs18}we painted a bus and drove out into the desert.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.63,0:06:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我真希望你能和我们在一起\N{\fnArial\fs18}I wish you would've stayed with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.60,0:06:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 Willow 做人要向前看\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, Willow. It was time for us to move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.12,0:06:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,那只是你的看法\N{\fnArial\fs18}That's what you want to call it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.21,0:06:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- 什么? - 亲爱的\N{\fnArial\fs18}- What? - Honey...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.33,0:06:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你什么意思嘛 Coyote?\N{\fnArial\fs18}What do you mean, Coyote?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.09,0:06:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么 我爱大家\N{\fnArial\fs18}Nothing, I love you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.76,0:06:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,只是我还记着你曾经的模样 仅此而已\N{\fnArial\fs18}It's just, I remember you as you were, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.06,0:06:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,实际上我们还是老样子\N{\fnArial\fs18}We're still that way, deep down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.57,0:06:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,对呀 亲 我们还是老样子\N{\fnArial\fs18}Yeah, man! We're still that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.03,0:06:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,什么样子?\N{\fnArial\fs18}What way?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.06,0:06:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,摆脱肤浅的由利益主导的文化价值体系\N{\fnArial\fs18}Free of the shallow, superficial value system of a profit-driven culture
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.10,0:06:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,已经是大错特错了\N{\fnArial\fs18}gone terribly, terribly wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.04,0:06:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,当然啦 我们就是这种人嘛\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, sure, we're that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.40,0:06:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我能和老屋主夫人说话么?\N{\fnArial\fs18}May I speak to the old lady of the house?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.47,0:06:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Daria 你在哪呀?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Daria, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.06,0:06:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,在Jane家 我能在她家过夜吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Jane's. Can I stay over?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.28,0:06:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我本来是想让你认识一下我们的朋友\N{\fnArial\fs18}I was hoping you would want to get to know our friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.21,0:06:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我苍老的灵魂已经在前世和他们相识了\N{\fnArial\fs18}My old soul has already made their acquaintance in a previous lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.08,0:06:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 这样的话就能给Ethan腾出点空间了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Well, that does free up some space for Ethan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.44,0:07:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,他睡客房 我能让Willow和Coyote睡你的房间\N{\fnArial\fs18}He can take the guest room, and I can put Willow and Coyote in your room.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.06,0:07:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你要让他们睡我的房间?\N{\fnArial\fs18}You're going to put them in my room?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.85,0:07:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你最好把他们绑在床上以防他们漂走\N{\fnArial\fs18}You better tether them to the bed so they don't float away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.03,0:07:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来《呕心小世界》恐怖故事:\N{\fnArial\fs18}A nightmare story of an enchanted kiss gone horribly wrong,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.72,0:07:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,大错特错的魔力之吻\N{\fnArial\fs18}when Sick, Sad World returns.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.83,0:07:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,搞定 我能在这睡了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Okay, I can stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.42,0:07:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你有什么能让我穿的睡衣么?\N{\fnArial\fs18}You have anything for me to sleep in?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.95,0:07:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,甭谢我 谢奶奶\N{\fnArial\fs18}Don't thank me. Thank Grandma.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.05,0:07:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,还有这呢 我们安置Daria的房间\N{\fnArial\fs18}And this, is where we keep Daria.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.63,0:07:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,酷 告诉我爸妈我就睡这里\N{\fnArial\fs18}Cool. Tell Mom and Dad I'm sleeping here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.82,0:07:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,一旦你能把所有身外之物都塞进背包里\N{\fnArial\fs18}Once you could fit all your worldly possessions into a backpack.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.98,0:07:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,一条牛仔裤 一些T恤 一本《偷走这本书》\N{\fnArial\fs18}Pair of jeans, a few T-shirts, a copy of Steal This Book.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.98,0:07:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs26\an8}书籍简介: 如何利用现存的体制谋生及电话偷窃术\N作者Abbie Hoffman 著名反文化人士 "雅皮士"领导人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.78,0:07:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来 瞧瞧你自己\N{\fnArial\fs18}And now, look at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.09,0:07:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,资本主义的拉拉队长 穿西装的叛徒 该死\N{\fnArial\fs18}A capitalist cheerleader, a sellout in a monkey suit! Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.12,0:07:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,是时候翻身做主人了\N{\fnArial\fs18}It's time to take a stand!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.87,0:07:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,明天绝不剃胡子\N{\fnArial\fs18}You're not gonna shave tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.32,0:07:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托 Jakey 让别人也用用厕所嘛\N{\fnArial\fs18}Come on, Jakey, let someone else have a turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.00,0:07:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- Helen 你觉得"我的青春小鸟一去不回来"吗? - 当然不是啦\N{\fnArial\fs18}- Helen, do you think I'm past my prime? - Of course not. 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.04,0:08:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你还是那么年轻有力\N{\fnArial\fs18}You're still quite the young buck.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.85,0:08:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么说呢 帅哥老了反而更帅\N{\fnArial\fs18}Anyway, good looking men get even handsomer as they mature.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.48,0:08:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 真可惜女人不是这样\N{\fnArial\fs18}Woo! Too bad it's not the same for women!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.66,0:08:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,好多了 这下我啥都看不到\N{\fnArial\fs18}That's better. Now I can't see a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.66,0:08:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,明天可是个大日子\N{\fnArial\fs18}Big day tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.13,0:08:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,六点叫你起床 安安\N{\fnArial\fs18}We'll wake you at six. 'Night.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.66,0:08:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安\N{\fnArial\fs18}Good night!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.38,0:08:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,安安 明早见\N{\fnArial\fs18}'Night, see you in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.75,0:08:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,六点再过来\N{\fnArial\fs18}Come back at six.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.77,0:08:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,已经六点啦\N{\fnArial\fs18}It is six.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.90,0:08:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那你怎么能这么精神?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Then how come you're so damn chipper?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.38,0:08:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,熬夜可比早起简单多了\N{\fnArial\fs18}It was easier to stay up all night than to wake up early.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.85,0:08:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我们先去把东西搬上货车\N{\fnArial\fs18}We'll load the van.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.22,0:08:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,货车?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Van?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.07,0:08:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你懂的 坦克\N{\fnArial\fs18}You know, the Tank.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.94,0:08:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,太好喽\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, goody.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.82,0:08:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,他们走了吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Are they gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.49,0:08:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,别忘记带上钱\N{\fnArial\fs18}Don't forget some money.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.88,0:08:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 奶奶不是有件同款睡袍吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Hey, doesn't Grandma have a nightgown like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.10,0:08:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我要把这个分到"自我放逐的装逼货"还是"怀才不遇"里?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Should I file this under "self-indulgent posers" or "underrated geniuses"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.44,0:09:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,问Trent或Jesse 随便问一个最早起床的人啦\N{\fnArial\fs18}Ask Trent or Jesse, whichever one wakes up first.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.95,0:09:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我猜之所以叫"跳蚤"市场 是因为它会让你想"逃走"\N{\fnArial\fs18}I guess they call it a flea market because it makes you want to flee.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.45,0:09:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,好了啦 放轻松 我们今天会棒棒哒\N{\fnArial\fs18}Come on, relax. We're going to do well today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.85,0:09:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的摊位有地理优势\N{\fnArial\fs18}We've got a choice location.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.46,0:09:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs26\an8}爱国者马桶盖套
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.70,0:09:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我想买雪球\N{\fnArial\fs18}I'm looking for snow domes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.35,0:09:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你们有卖的么?\N{\fnArial\fs18}You got any, girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.61,0:09:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 夫人\N{\fnArial\fs18}Sorry, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.55,0:09:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我们只卖这些外星人留下来的奇怪圆盘唱片\N{\fnArial\fs18}All we have are these strange, flat discs the aliens left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.51,0:09:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,外星人你造吧?\N{\fnArial\fs18}You know about the aliens, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.14,0:09:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你很享受参与公众工作嘛?\N{\fnArial\fs18}You enjoy working with the public, don't you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.42,0:09:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好\N{\fnArial\fs18}Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.49,0:09:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,向崭新的Jake问好\N{\fnArial\fs18}Say hello to a new Jake.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.96,0:09:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,就是以前的那个Jake\N{\fnArial\fs18}The old Jake!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.34,0:09:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,好久不见的Jake\N{\fnArial\fs18}The Jake you haven't seen for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.87,0:09:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,向饼干模具公司的Jake说再见\N{\fnArial\fs18}And goodbye to cookie-cutter corporate guy Jake.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.87,0:09:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs26\an8}cookie-cutter又为千篇一律 此处Jake说的是这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.38,0:09:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,那个Jake已经走啦 离开啦 不干啦\N{\fnArial\fs18}That Jake is gone, gone, gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.14,0:09:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你该不会是辞职了吧?\N{\fnArial\fs18}You didn't quit your job, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.90,0:09:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,没啦 我在留胡子呢\N{\fnArial\fs18}No, I'm growing a beard again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.03,0:09:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,那挺好的 亲爱的\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh! That's great, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.00,0:10:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 Quinn 你觉得我的新造型咋样?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Hey, Quinn! How do you like my, new look?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.96,0:10:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,老爸 你是在留山羊胡吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Dad, are you growing a goatee?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.77,0:10:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,有够老土的\N{\fnArial\fs18}That's so two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.95,0:10:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,对吧 Ethan?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Right, Ethan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.95,0:10:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得现在精力真集中\N{\fnArial\fs18}I really feel centered now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.11,0:10:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- 胡子挺不错 - 谢谢\N{\fnArial\fs18}- Nice whiskers. - Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.45,0:10:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,这儿有点挤了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Um, it's kind of getting crowded in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.09,0:10:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我还是和Ethan出去吃早餐吧\N{\fnArial\fs18}Why don't Ethan and I go out for breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.16,0:10:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你们就能好好坐一起追忆当年啦\N{\fnArial\fs18}You guys can sit around and remember things.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.47,0:10:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,早餐? 我还以为要吃午餐了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Breakfast? I thought it was lunch time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.51,0:10:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我回去睡觉了\N{\fnArial\fs18}I'm going back to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.44,0:10:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你干嘛盯着我哥看?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Why are you staring at my brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.50,0:10:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,无私的关心\N{\fnArial\fs18}Selfless concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.13,0:10:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为他嗝屁了\N{\fnArial\fs18}I think he stopped breathing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.91,0:10:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,他在休眠呢\N{\fnArial\fs18}Nah, he's entering a dormant stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.09,0:10:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,大概十年后他就能破茧成蝶了\N{\fnArial\fs18}In about ten years he should emerge as a butterfly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.66,0:10:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我猜你只能独守空房了\N{\fnArial\fs18}I guess you're gonna wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.42,0:10:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你们好呀 女士们\N{\fnArial\fs18}Hello, ladies!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.26,0:10:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我咋不知道你们也是主办人呢\N{\fnArial\fs18}I didn't know you were of an entrepreneur bent.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.37,0:10:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,也许你们会友善地让我瞧瞧商品?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Perhaps you would be so kind as to show me your goods?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.83,0:10:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,呕男 你在这干嘛?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Upchuck, what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.56,0:10:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我在找快餐奖赏的圣杯\N{\fnArial\fs18}I am on a quest for the Holy Grail of fast food premiums.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.83,0:11:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,一个1985年加州产的仿真葡萄干橡胶套\N{\fnArial\fs18}A complete 1985 California Raisins posable eraser set.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.12,0:11:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,要完好无损的才行\N{\fnArial\fs18}Only mint condition will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.56,0:11:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你的投资商么?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Your investors?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.04,0:11:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,沉默搭档\N{\fnArial\fs18}Silent partners.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.58,0:11:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你们有没有《回头是岸》的原声带?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Do you by any chance have the cast recording of Somebody Up There Likes Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.58,0:11:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs26\an8}拳王Rocky Graziano的传记电影
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.62,0:11:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,没有 不过我们有《下面的人才不》\N{\fnArial\fs18}No, but we do have Somebody Down Here Doesn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.64,0:11:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我在想也许我能给你们一些销售建议\N{\fnArial\fs18}I wonder if I may provide you gals with a lesson in salesmanship.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.04,0:11:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你们将终身受益哟\N{\fnArial\fs18}It's a once in a lifetime offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.70,0:11:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,两生受益怎么样?\N{\fnArial\fs18}How about once in two lifetimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.82,0:11:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,好啦 现在就让这货告诉我们咋做\N{\fnArial\fs18}Now, now, let the boy show us how to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.43,0:11:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就不用干了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Then we won't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.76,0:11:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,又回到我手上了\N{\fnArial\fs18}It's all coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.31,0:11:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,想试试吗 亲爱的?\N{\fnArial\fs18}You wanna try, honey?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.51,0:11:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,真恶心 狗的口水 那只野兽\N{\fnArial\fs18}Ugh, dog drool. That beast!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.37,0:11:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,出去\N{\fnArial\fs18}Outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.10,0:11:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你好? Eric?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Hello? Eric?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.90,0:11:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,什么? 他们要把听证提前到这周?\N{\fnArial\fs18}What? They moved the hearing up to this week?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.17,0:11:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我20分钟内赶不过去呀\N{\fnArial\fs18}I can be there in 20 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.56,0:11:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,说到紧张之处了啊\N{\fnArial\fs18}Talk about uptight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.20,0:11:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,放轻松\N{\fnArial\fs18}Mellow out, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.03,0:11:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么急事不能等到周一说\N{\fnArial\fs18}Nothing's so important that it can't wait till Monday,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.84,0:12:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你周末还在公司里关着自己干嘛呀?\N{\fnArial\fs18}what are you doing in the corporate cage on the weekend?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.15,0:12:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不去公园里散散步\N{\fnArial\fs18}Don't take a walk in the park.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.35,0:12:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这就对了 亲爱的\N{\fnArial\fs18}Right on, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.35,0:12:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你还保留着优先权呀\N{\fnArial\fs18}You still have your priorities.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.75,0:12:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,谁要接飞盘? 来呀 Leary\N{\fnArial\fs18}Who's up for frisbee? Come on, Leary!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.90,0:12:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Eric 就是啦 我当然是在讲笑\N{\fnArial\fs18}Eric? Yes, of course I was kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.48,0:12:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,瞧见了么 女士们\N{\fnArial\fs18}You see, ladies,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.02,0:12:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不用正确方法关闭交易\N{\fnArial\fs18}trying to close a sale without the proper technique
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.92,0:12:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,就像玩牌不用一整副牌\N{\fnArial\fs18}is like playing cards without a full deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.00,0:12:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你得把顾客当成上帝\N{\fnArial\fs18}You must treat your customers like a king.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.75,0:12:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是取胜的花招\N{\fnArial\fs18}This is the ace up your sleeves.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.43,0:12:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不这样做的话就是小丑牌 手里就只剩J了\N{\fnArial\fs18}You're a joker if you don't, and you'll be left with jack.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.52,0:12:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,讲到两生受益的干货再叫醒我\N{\fnArial\fs18}Wake me when you get to the twos.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.58,0:12:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,罗斯福?\N{\fnArial\fs18}FDR?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.53,0:12:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不 先生 我的马桶盖套上才没有什么社会主义者\N{\fnArial\fs18}No, sir, you won't find socialists on any of my toilet seats.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.87,0:12:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,现在看哥亲身示范\N{\fnArial\fs18}Now, watch a pro in action.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.51,0:12:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 DeMartino老师\N{\fnArial\fs18}Hey! Mr. DeMartino!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.64,0:12:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 Charles Ruttheimer\N{\fnArial\fs18}Well, Charles Ruttheimer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.43,0:12:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,什么事 Charles?\N{\fnArial\fs18}What is it, Charles?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.85,0:12:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,作为栽培和育种的一员\N{\fnArial\fs18}As a man of culture and breeding,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.48,0:13:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我想您也许会对我们的部分听觉佳作感兴趣\N{\fnArial\fs18}I thought you might be interested in some of our audio gems.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.62,0:13:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你在尝试做可悲的奉承么 Ruttheimer先生?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Is this a pathetic attempt at flattery, Mr. Ruttheimer?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.10,0:13:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你精心蓄谋那么明显的烟雾弹\N{\fnArial\fs18}An obvious smoke screen for your calculated attempt
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.28,0:13:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,就是想把我从每周照看一群蠢货赚来的钱\N{\fnArial\fs18}at separate me from the payments I receive each week for babysitting
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.36,0:13:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,夺走吧?!\N{\fnArial\fs18}a bunch of determined idiots?!?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.72,0:13:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是想向你推销些唱片....\N{\fnArial\fs18}I just wanted to sell you some records...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.77,0:13:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,有没有Annette Funicello的?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Got anything by Annette Funicello?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.77,0:13:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs26\an8}首批米老鼠俱乐部成员之一
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.68,0:13:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 伙计 你修完这辆宝贝后\N{\fnArial\fs18}Hey, man, after you get this baby fixed up,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.36,0:13:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我们一起去俱乐部玩上几把咋样?\N{\fnArial\fs18}what do you say we go down to the club and play a round?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.61,0:13:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,高尔夫球场就是生态灾难地\N{\fnArial\fs18}The golf course is an ecological disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.58,0:13:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么 你不懂怎么挥杆吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}What, you got trouble with your swing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.10,0:13:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,给 你们小子们也许想来点提神的\N{\fnArial\fs18}Here, we thought you boys might like some refreshments.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.35,0:13:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,自制浆果汁\N{\fnArial\fs18}Home-bottled berry juice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.23,0:13:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要去堆肥\N{\fnArial\fs18}We're going to start a compost pile.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.45,0:13:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,一定很好玩吧?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Won't that be fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.15,0:13:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 这玩意真带劲\N{\fnArial\fs18}Wow! This is strong stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.49,0:13:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,放了天然的果胶\N{\fnArial\fs18}It's got natural pectins.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.70,0:13:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱果胶\N{\fnArial\fs18}I love pectins!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.17,0:13:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是最低价?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Is this the best you can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.04,0:13:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,是的...\N{\fnArial\fs18}'Fraid so...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.75,0:13:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,那好吧 我不买了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Well then, I guess I'm just going to have to walk away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.51,0:13:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我要走咯....\N{\fnArial\fs18}I'm walking...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.36,0:13:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,好呗 50美分\N{\fnArial\fs18}Okay, fifty cents.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.92,0:14:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢亲\N{\fnArial\fs18}Thanks, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.10,0:14:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我的佣金呢?\N{\fnArial\fs18}What about my commission?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.12,0:14:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 我们可是免费栽培你耶\N{\fnArial\fs18}Hey, we're training you for free.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.56,0:14:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 Trent 既然你回魂了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Well, Trent, now that you've returned to the land of the living,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.44,0:14:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,也许你和Daria能去买点苏打\N{\fnArial\fs18}maybe you and Daria can go get us some soda.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.21,0:14:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,要含咖啡因的?\N{\fnArial\fs18}With caffeine?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.64,0:14:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题 来呀?\N{\fnArial\fs18}No problem. Coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.42,0:14:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\fnArial\fs18}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.17,0:14:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,慢慢来\N{\fnArial\fs18}Take your time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.62,0:14:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我想吃点汉堡\N{\fnArial\fs18}I could use a burger.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.56,0:14:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我也去\N{\fnArial\fs18}I'll go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.70,0:14:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,呕霸 你能看会摊么?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Upchuck, can you handle the booth?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.53,0:14:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我什么都能搞定 小姐\N{\fnArial\fs18}I can handle much more than that, missy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.06,0:14:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,请问 那是《一瞥所见》的复刻版?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Excuse me! But is that a vintage copy of Eyefull?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.58,0:14:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,1962年的\N{\fnArial\fs18}1962.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.35,0:14:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你哪里找到这么一个宝贝?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Where did you find such a treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.16,0:14:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,那边的摊位\N{\fnArial\fs18}That booth over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.45,0:14:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,没事 我来付\N{\fnArial\fs18}That's okay, I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.50,0:14:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- 欠你啦 - 下次还\N{\fnArial\fs18}- I owe you one, then. - Next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.39,0:14:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 Janey说你这周都在躲你爸妈的朋友?\N{\fnArial\fs18}So, Janey says you're avoiding your parent's friends this weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.84,0:15:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,他们阳光活力的60年代乐观主义\N{\fnArial\fs18}Their sunny Sixties optimism
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.00,0:15:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,快要抵消掉我90年代的玩世不恭了\N{\fnArial\fs18}tends to cancel out my bitter Nineties cynicism.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.07,0:15:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,赖死不走的嬉皮士?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Holdover hippies?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.73,0:15:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 他们是"一切从简"的狂热崇拜者\N{\fnArial\fs18}Yeah. They're big believers in the concept of voluntary simplicity.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.90,0:15:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我也得用上那词\N{\fnArial\fs18}I gotta use that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.43,0:15:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,比"一贫如洗"好听多了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Sounds much better than broke.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.80,0:15:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我猜你得给他们点权利\N{\fnArial\fs18}I guess you gotta give them some credit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.07,0:15:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,民事权利 环境保护 妇女运动\N{\fnArial\fs18}Civil rights, environmentalism, the women's movement.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.36,0:15:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,给他们点那个年代人们信赖的东西\N{\fnArial\fs18}People believed in stuff back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.39,0:15:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\fnArial\fs18}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.42,0:15:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,那有什么不对?\N{\fnArial\fs18}What's up with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.99,0:15:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你在想什么 不过我可是顶天立地的牛人了\N{\fnArial\fs18}I know what you're thinking, but I've turned into the man!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.69,0:15:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我从来没称过你牛人 亲\N{\fnArial\fs18}I'd never call you the man, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.20,0:15:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,人 也许有 可不牛\N{\fnArial\fs18}Man, maybe, but not the man.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.55,0:15:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我讨厌这傻缺的生锈废物\N{\fnArial\fs18}I hate this stupid rusty piece of junk!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.69,0:15:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,而且我厌倦了买散装食品\N{\fnArial\fs18}And I'm tired of buying food in bulk!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.77,0:15:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,每次上完厕所都不能冲 因为会浪费水资源\N{\fnArial\fs18}And not flushing every time I go because it wastes water!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.99,0:15:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我还年轻 我的信仰都怎么了?\N{\fnArial\fs18}I'm still young. What happened to my beliefs?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.09,0:15:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,做能解决问题的人 不做制造麻烦的人 又怎么了?\N{\fnArial\fs18}What happened to being part of the solution, not part of the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.96,0:15:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我恨死揉面团了\N{\fnArial\fs18}I hate kneading bread.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.62,0:15:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯?\N{\fnArial\fs18}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.55,0:15:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我... 恨死... 揉... 面团啦\N{\fnArial\fs18}I... hate... kneading... bread!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.96,0:16:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,该死\N{\fnArial\fs18}Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.32,0:16:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 Willow 来\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh Willow! Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.88,0:16:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,亲 你能教我打高尔夫么?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Man, can you teach me how to play golf?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.21,0:16:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,当然可以 亲\N{\fnArial\fs18}Of course I can, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.61,0:16:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我们能坐着这小推车转悠转悠么?\N{\fnArial\fs18}And can we ride around on those little carts?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.90,0:16:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题 伙计\N{\fnArial\fs18}Sure thing, pal!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.65,0:16:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 有机化肥的蒸气浴嘛? 真酷耶\N{\fnArial\fs18}Hey, some kind of organic nutrient steam bath, right? Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.00,0:16:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Jake 我们在垃圾堆里摔倒啦 感觉自己就像猪\N{\fnArial\fs18}Jake, we fell on our asses in a pile of garbage. I feel like a hog.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.94,0:16:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,猪 我想死培根了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Hog! I miss bacon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.89,0:16:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 谢谢你如此的关心\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, thanks so much for your concern!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.76,0:16:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 妹子们好像在闹革命哟\N{\fnArial\fs18}Wow, sounds like the girls are getting liberated.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.52,0:16:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,酷\N{\fnArial\fs18}Cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.31,0:16:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,老爸 浆果汁又发酵了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Dad, the berry juice fermented again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.01,0:16:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,小心点\N{\fnArial\fs18}You gotta watch that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.79,0:16:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧 我给你买个泥浆杯\N{\fnArial\fs18}Come on, I'll buy you a slush cup.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.99,0:16:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,真是时候\N{\fnArial\fs18}It's about time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.26,0:16:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,身上有钱没?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Got any money?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.65,0:16:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我的剃须刀呢?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Where's my razor?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.20,0:16:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你瞧 在我看来\N{\fnArial\fs18}You see, my theory is
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.32,0:16:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,原始的狩猎本能在现代社会可没有出路\N{\fnArial\fs18}that our primitive hunting instinct has no outlet in modern society.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.31,0:16:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,酷\N{\fnArial\fs18}Cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.74,0:16:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,所以说 与其说跟踪动物\N{\fnArial\fs18}So, rather than stalking animals,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.65,0:17:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,倒不如说是购物和寻找猎物\N{\fnArial\fs18}we substitute the shopping experience, and hunt for objects.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.52,0:17:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,酷\N{\fnArial\fs18}Cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.10,0:17:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,然后呢 Jesse 当我们睡着\N{\fnArial\fs18}And then, Jesse, while we're asleep,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.02,0:17:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,猎物就会醒来策划阴谋 要侵略我们的文明\N{\fnArial\fs18}the objects come to life and plot their secret take over our civilization.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.97,0:17:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,2007年4月1号 就是他们暴动的日子\N{\fnArial\fs18}April 1st, 2007. That's the day they make their move!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.19,0:17:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,酷\N{\fnArial\fs18}Cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.14,0:17:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fnArial\fs18}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.95,0:17:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这些人都在交换着没用的垃圾\N{\fnArial\fs18}All these people swapping useless junk.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.83,0:17:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeager一家人也许掌握了些情况\N{\fnArial\fs18}Maybe the Yeagers are onto something.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.13,0:17:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,至少他们没有陷入无止尽的消费里\N{\fnArial\fs18}At least they're not caught up in a constant state of consumer frenzy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.51,0:17:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我猜如果你还是要执着一些六十年代的事物\N{\fnArial\fs18}Yeah, I guess if you're gonna insist on holding on to something from the Sixties,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.68,0:17:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,爱与和平可比午餐盒好多了\N{\fnArial\fs18}peace and love beats a Get Smart lunchbox.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.43,0:17:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,特别是里面还放着午餐的话\N{\fnArial\fs18}Especially if the lunch is still in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.73,0:17:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧 去替Jesse和Jane的班吧\N{\fnArial\fs18}Well, let's go give Jesse and Jane a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.23,0:17:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,太晚了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.63,0:17:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,谁在看摊呀?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Who's watching the booth?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.37,0:17:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,呕男\N{\fnArial\fs18}Upchuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.26,0:17:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不是吧\N{\fnArial\fs18}I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.80,0:17:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,看这 Demartino老师\N{\fnArial\fs18}Here, Mr. Demartino!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.34,0:17:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我找到另一期的《单身汉机密》\N{\fnArial\fs18}I found another issue of Bachelor Confidential!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.73,0:17:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你弥补了过错 Charles\N{\fnArial\fs18}You have redeemed yourself, Charles.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.09,0:18:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,至少不用搬那么多货回去啦?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Less to carry home?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.71,0:18:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我们还剩三张Boston乐队的唱片\N{\fnArial\fs18}Well, we do have three copies left to "Boston."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.77,0:18:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,至少我们不是贪钱的资本主义猪 对吧 Daria?\N{\fnArial\fs18}At least we're not money grabbing capitalist pigs, right, Daria?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.77,0:18:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 我们只是一切从简的中坚分子\N{\fnArial\fs18}Yeah, we're just hard core believers in voluntary simplicity.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.50,0:18:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不 警察从没正式起诉过他们\N{\fnArial\fs18}No, they never formally charged them,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.43,0:18:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不过第二天就把他们关大牢里去了\N{\fnArial\fs18}they did keep them there in jail for the next day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.91,0:18:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 我的眉笔哪去了?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Hey, where's my eyebrow pencil?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.47,0:18:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,这猛料至少也得值20块钱\N{\fnArial\fs18}This has gotta be worth at least twenty bucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.02,0:18:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 再说一遍我妈是怎么揍警察的?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Now, tell me again about how Mom punched out the cop.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.09,0:18:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你确定你不要了吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}You're sure you don't want this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.98,0:18:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我从来没用过呢\N{\fnArial\fs18}I never use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.15,0:18:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,这能大大缩短我给Ethan和Coyote烘焙的时间\N{\fnArial\fs18}This will cut way down on the time I spending baking for Ethan and Coyote.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.71,0:18:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,大姐 瞧瞧冷冻的贝果\N{\fnArial\fs18}Sister, meet the frozen bagel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.71,0:18:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs26\an8}又称百吉饼 传统的犹太面包圈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.24,0:18:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 亲们 天快黑啦\N{\fnArial\fs18}Hey, guys, it's getting dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.53,0:18:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你们什么时候进屋呀?\N{\fnArial\fs18}When are you going to come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.95,0:19:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,就快啦\N{\fnArial\fs18}In a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.19,0:19:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我在教Coyote怎么避免打出曲线球\N{\fnArial\fs18}I'm just showing Coyote how to drive without slicing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.88,0:19:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,有进步\N{\fnArial\fs18}Better!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.88,0:19:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,姑娘们 我期望你还吃得下饭\N{\fnArial\fs18}Girls, I expected you for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.11,0:19:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,在我正式下令关你们禁闭前 要不要解释一下你们的行踪?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Before I officially ground you, would you care to account for your whereabouts?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.32,0:19:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 不过首先 提点问题\N{\fnArial\fs18}Sure. But first, a few questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.96,0:19:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,问题一\N{\fnArial\fs18}Number one:
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.85,0:19:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,69年8月 你怎么会在Boulder市监狱呆了一晚?\N{\fnArial\fs18}why did you spend a night in jail in Boulder in August, 1969?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.89,0:19:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你的营销策划\N{\fnArial\fs18}Thanks for that marketing plan, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.89,0:19:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要去给彩虹吊床公司的懦夫们好看\N{\fnArial\fs18}We're going to kick the butts of those wimps over at Rainbow Hammocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.84,0:19:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 别留活口 大哥\N{\fnArial\fs18}Hey, take no prisoners, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.49,0:19:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,掠夺是天性\N{\fnArial\fs18}Predatory behavior is all natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.65,0:19:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Ethan?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Ethan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.45,0:19:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.25,0:19:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你都没说过人家很可爱嘛?\N{\fnArial\fs18}You never told me whether you thought I was, you know, cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.30,0:19:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 当然 你很可爱\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, well, sure, you're cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.75,0:19:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fnArial\fs18}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.92,0:19:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,是很... 你懂的... 在肤浅的层面...\N{\fnArial\fs18}In a, you know, shallow, superficial way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.17,0:19:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fnArial\fs18}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.44,0:19:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,要想不夸你 很难吧?\N{\fnArial\fs18}It's very hard not to compliment you, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.32,0:19:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Daria 你用不着这么说啦\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, Daria, you don't have to say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.20,0:20:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Daria 你觉得异地恋是不是挺好的?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Daria, do you think long-distance relationships are a good idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.55,0:20:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 为何我俩不试试?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Yeah. Why don't you and I try one?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.85,0:20:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你们懂的 孩子们 沉湎过去根本没有意义\N{\fnArial\fs18}You know, kids, it's pointless to try to go back in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.56,0:20:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你得活在当下 这就是老爸我现在要做的\N{\fnArial\fs18}You have to live in the present, and I'm going to start right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.71,0:20:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,第一步就是 扔掉我的所有黑胶唱片\N{\fnArial\fs18}First things first: I'm getting rid of all my vinyl records.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.40,0:20:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 Daria 你想要唱片吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Hey, Daria! You want 'em?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.42,0:20:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn迷你简汉真广标\fsp1\c&HE6ECE8&\pos(400,156)}欢迎微博关注\N\N{\fs28}@漫迪字幕组
